item.title: Complexity in public health
item.description: At the Copenhagen Health Complexity Center, we develop practical tools for analyzing complex health problems.

item.title: Health inequalities
item.description: Health inequalities are a major societal challenge, and evidence suggests that health inequality is established in childhood and may even transcend generations.

item.title: Young adult health
item.description: The vision of the Copenhagen Health Complexity Center is to understand real-world health complexities among young adults.
